Ms\": 24098,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"main_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Lead is confused - they're seeing all the workspaces (34 agent folders) in the GitHub repo instead of just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` folder. \\n\\nThis is because the GitHub repo `maiychrus25/setup-openclaw` actually contains the entire `v4-ecosystem-review` workspace, not just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` folder. The remote was set to push the whole `v4-ecosystem-review` directory, not just the `ahv-openclaw-setup` subdirectory.\\n\\nWait, no - I pushed from the `v4-ecosystem-review` directory, which contains ALL the agent workspaces. The remote `origin` was set to `git@github.com:maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git`, so ALL of `v4-ecosystem-review` was pushed there.\\n\\n\\nThat's exactly what happened - I pushed the entire `v4-ecosystem-review` directory to GitHub, so Lead is seeing all 34 agent workspaces instead of just the setup folder they needed. The setup-openclaw repo was just a subdirectory within that, not the whole thing.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Dạ **bị đẩy nhầm toàn bộ workspace lên** — vì em push từ thư mục cha `v4-ecosystem-review/`, không phải chỉ `ahv-openclaw-setup/`.\\n\\nTrên GitHub giờ chứa **34 workspaces + toàn bộ agent files** — không đúng. Lead cần xóa repo GitHub và tạo lại đúng.\\n\\n**Cách xử lý:**\\n\\n1. **Xóa repo** `setup-openclaw` trên GitHub\\n2. **Tạo repo mới** trên GitHub\\n3. **Xóa remote sai** trên máy:\\n```bash\\ngit remote remove origin\\n```\\n4. **Clone lại đúng folder**:\\n```bash\\n# Trên máy Lead, clone repo mới về\\ngit clone https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\\ncd setup-openclaw\\nnpm install\\nnode bin/ahv-setup.js\\n```\\n\\nTrên máy này (atu-ahv-ai006), repo đúng đã có sẵn tại:\\n```\\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/\\n```\\n\\nLead muốn em xử lý xóa repo trên GitLab/GitHub không?\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 611,\n            \"output\": 532,\n            \"totalTokens\": 143008,\n            \"cacheRead\": 141433,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 432,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776228252270,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e4a9e2e309272db3ce42e0474aacd\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"576f7fad\",\n            \"seq\": 1731\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607